                <h1>Do Traffic Violations Appear on Background Checks?</h1>
                <p>Traffic violations generally don't appear on a criminal background check, as they're typically considered civil offenses rather than criminal ones. However, serious violations like DUIs might show up, depending on local laws and the type of background check being conducted. Always check local regulations for specifics.</p>
